items.title: Awesome Dataviz
items.content_text:
### JavaScript tools / Maps

*   [L7 (⭐3.8k)](https://github.com/antvis/L7) - Large-scale WebGL-powered Geospatial Data Visualization analysis framework, maintained by Alibaba
*   [L7 Plot (⭐92)](https://github.com/antvis/L7Plot) - Geospatial Visualization Chart Library, maintained by Alibaba
*   [Dipper (⭐29)](https://github.com/antvis/dipper) - Map application development framework powered by L7, maintained by Alibaba.

### JavaScript tools / React

*   [Graphin (⭐1.1k)](https://github.com/antvis/Graphin) - Graph visualization library powered by React & Typescript (built on top of G6, maintained by Alibaba.

### Anime

- API: [Trace Moe](https://soruly.github.io/trace.moe-api/#/)

  Description: A useful tool to get the exact scene of an anime from a screenshot

  Auth: No

  HTTPS: Yes

  CORS: No



### Authentication & Authorization

- API: [Warrant](https://warrant.dev/)

  Description: APIs for authorization and access control

  Auth: `apiKey`

  HTTPS: Yes

  CORS: Yes
